= Definition Lists

Definition lists pair terms with their definitions or descriptions.

== Basic Definition List

CPU:: The brain of the computer.
RAM:: Temporarily stores information the CPU uses during operation.
Hard drive:: Permanent storage for operating system and/or user files.

== Definition List with Title

.Definition List: Computer Components
CPU:: Central Processing Unit - executes instructions
RAM:: Random Access Memory - temporary storage
SSD:: Solid State Drive - fast permanent storage

== Horizontal Definition List

[horizontal]
CPU:: The brain of the computer.
RAM:: Temporarily stores information.
Hard drive:: Permanent storage.

== Definition List with Multiple Definitions

Term:: First definition
Term:: Second definition
Term:: Third definition

== Definition List with Complex Content

Operating System::
An operating system manages computer hardware and software resources.

It provides common services for computer programs.

Programming Language::
A programming language is a formal language used to write computer programs.

Examples include:
* Python
* JavaScript
* Ruby

== Nested Definition Lists

Computer::
Hardware:: Physical components of a computer
Software:: Programs and data that run on hardware

Software::
Operating System:: Manages hardware resources
Applications:: Programs for specific tasks

== Definition List with Formatting

*Bold Term*:: Definition with *bold* and _italic_ text.

`Code Term`:: Definition explaining the code term.

Link Term:: Definition with a https://example.com[link].

